tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE influencer_content_calendar (
    post_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    post_title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    post_date DATE NOT NULL,
    post_content TEXT,
    collaboration_partner VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE influencer_profiles (
  influencer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  influencer_name VARCHAR(100),
  followers_count INT,
  bio TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE post_schedule (
  post_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  influencer_id INT,
  post_content TEXT,
  post_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE collaborations (
  collaboration_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  influencer_id INT,
  brand_name VARCHAR(100),
  collaboration_type VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE influencer_profiles (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(50),
    email VARCHAR(100),
    followers INT
)

CREATE TABLE posts (
    post_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    post_title VARCHAR(100),
    post_content TEXT,
    post_date DATE,
    influencer_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (influencer_id) REFERENCES influencer_profiles(id)
)

CREATE TABLE collaborations (
    collaboration_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    collaboration_name VARCHAR(100),
    collaboration_description TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    influencer_id INT,
    partner_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (influencer_id) REFERENCES influencer_profiles(id),
    FOREIGN KEY (partner_id) REFERENCES influencer_profiles(id)
)

CREATE TABLE hashtags (
    hashtag_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    hashtag_name VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE influencer_profiles (
    influencer_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    influencer_name TEXT, 
    followers_count INT
)

CREATE TABLE post_schedule (
    schedule_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    influencer_id INT, 
    post_datetime TIMESTAMP, 
    post_content TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE collaboration_requests (
    request_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    influencer_id INT, 
    brand_name TEXT, 
    collaboration_type TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE campaign_performance (
    campaign_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    influencer_id INT, 
    campaign_name TEXT, 
    engagement_rate DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE influencer_contacts (
    contact_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    influencer_id INT, 
    contact_name TEXT, 
    contact_email TEXT
)
